  "title": "COMMERCIAL SALES ENGINEER (VALVE)",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Responsibilities</strong></u></p>\n<p>1. Reviewing project specifications and preparing sales quotations</p>\n<p>2. To provide pre-sales and technical support to customers</p>\n<p>3. Liaising with internal departments to meet delivery dates</p>\n<p>4. To perform ad-hoc assignments if require</p>\n<p>5. To source and perform negotiation with mills/suppliers</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p>\n<p>1. Minimum Degree/diploma in any engineering</p>\n<p>2. Internal sales experience in valves related products, in the oil and gas/marine and offshore industries is mandatory, 3 to 5 years similar working experience (minimum)</p>\n<p>3. Excellent interpersonal and communication skill</p>\n<p>4. Good project management skills and customer service orientate</p>\n<p>5. Have a strong sense of urgency, meticulous, excellent follow up skills and negotiation skills</p>\n<p>6. Able to work under pressure and meet tight datelines</p>\n<p>7. Exposure in project management</p>",
